31:27.553 --> 31:30.723
You'll end up in jail for a long time,
I have the strangest feeling.

31:30.807 --> 31:33.434
You're jealous 'cause I'm gonna stay a cop.

31:33.726 --> 31:36.604
What the fuck is this? Go back to work.

31:42.402 --> 31:43.820
Here we go.

32:50.386 --> 32:52.305
What are you thinking?

33:13.493 --> 33:15.912
Isn't this your mother's church?

33:16.371 --> 33:19.832
