in the choir.

33:41.938 --> 33:43.314
Hey, Nico!

33:43.731 --> 33:45.441
I can't believe you're in church
without your family.

33:45.525 --> 33:46.776
Hello, Father. How are you?

33:46.859 --> 33:48.528
