33:55.952 --> 33:57.495
God, it's good you're here.

33:57.579 --> 34:00.039
If you got a few minutes,
there's something I'd like to show you.

34:00.123 --> 34:01.374
Please.

34:02.834 --> 34:05.837
I haven't been down here since I was a kid.

34:15.972 --> 34:17.431
What's this?

34:17.639 --> 34:19.891
The rats are getting bigger.

34:21.436 --> 34:25.440
