35:00.183 --> 35:01.726
These are friends.

35:01.809 --> 35:04.020
Father Tomasino, this is Nico.

35:04.145 --> 35:05.647
{y:i}- Mucho gusto, Padre.
- How do you do?

35:05.730 --> 35:07.732
- Sister Mary.
- Hi, Nico.

35:08.191 --> 35:10.151
- Delores.
- How do you do, Father?

35:10.235 --> 35:12.487
{y:i}- Señora, mucho gusto.
- Hello.

35:13.863 --> 35:17.992
My friend, Father Tomasino,
is working with the sanctuary movement.

35:18.076 --> 35:19.369
He's visiting...

35:19.452 --> 35:23.706
