Nico, we must go.

35:29.712 --> 35:30.964
{y:i}Gracias.

35:33.007 --> 35:34.926
Nice meeting you, sir.

35:36.511 --> 35:37.637
Bye-bye.

35:52.527 --> 35:55.697
- How long have those people been here?
- Too long.

35:55.780 --> 35:58.575
At least the children go to our school.

35:59.242 --> 36:01.452
Who do you think broke into the room?

36:01.536 --> 36:04.956
Kids, maybe. Maybe worse.
It's not the first time.

36:06.249 --> 36:08.793
Would you like us to send a car
to check on you?

36:08.876 --> 36:11.838
No, please. Police frighten these people.

36:12.922 --> 36:15.925
I know what you mean.
They frighten me, too.

36:17.594 --> 36:21.055
