36:40.783 --> 36:42.619
He's got your number!

36:43.244 --> 36:47.957
- Is that your impression of police officers?
- I want to see you in church Sunday, okay?

36:48.041 --> 36:51.002
I feel better when you're in church, okay?

36:51.252 --> 36:53.630
You don't show up, I'll call your mother!

36:53.713 --> 36:56.132
