37:29.666 --> 37:31.793
...about all of mankind...

37:33.670 --> 37:35.004
...as one.

37:35.672 --> 37:37.966
Now, we have an obligation...

37:38.716 --> 37:41.219
...to find out what is the truth.

37:43.012 --> 37:45.807
We need to study. We need to question.

37:46.683 --> 37:49.644
We need to read and we need to find out...

37:49.727 --> 37:52.313
...what they are doing in our name.

37:55.358 --> 37:58.236
And we must support those brave souls...

37:59.320 --> 38:00.863
...who seek...

38:01.906 --> 38:03.324
...the truth.

38:05.368 --> 38:07.203
God bless us. Amen.

38:57.545 --> 38:58.880
Get down!

39:48.304 --> 39:50.682
There's nothing else we can do.

39:54.435 --> 39:56.688
Lord God, Heavenly Father...

39:56.813 --> 40:01.317
...receive the soul of our dear
departed friend, Father Joseph Gennaro.

40:06.447 --> 40:07.490
Come on.

40:17.166 --> 40:20.753
Get a list of everybody treated here today.
Everybody.

40:20.837 --> 40:23.089
Find those sanctuary people...

40:23.172 --> 40:26.843
...the ones we found hiding
in the bottom of the church.

40:27.176 --> 40:31.431
I want to know where they're from
and who might want to harm them.

40:32.974 --> 40:34.100
Where are you gonna be?

40:34.183 --> 40:36.978
Just stay by the radio. I'll find you.

40:54.203 --> 40:56.497
- He didn't make it.
- Oh, Nico!

40:56.956 --> 40:58.082
Oh, no!

41:09.302 --> 41:12.555
Lieutenant Strozah, these are FBI agents:
Halloran, Neeley.

41:18.061 --> 41:22.232
Sweetheart, go to the car.
I'll be right there, okay? Take Mama.

41:27.570 --> 41:30.448
Nico, you okay? How's the family doing?

41:31.908 --> 41:34.911
