46:42.758 --> 46:44.093
Fuck him up!

46:44.176 --> 46:45.845
You motherfucker!

47:42.735 --> 47:45.446
Don't kill me! Please don't kill me!

47:46.405 --> 47:47.782
- Who sent you?
- Nobody!

47:47.865 --> 47:50.201
