47:53.871 --> 47:55.456
Jimmy Costanza!

47:57.166 --> 48:01.379
If I find out you're lying, I'll come back
and kill you in your own kitchen.

48:01.462 --> 48:02.672
Salvano!

48:03.256 --> 48:04.757
Bautista Salvano!

48:07.677 --> 48:10.805
- That's my buddy, man.
- Yeah, man, I know him.

48:13.933 --> 48:15.476
Sic him, Bulldog.

48:15.559 --> 48:18.813
- Why are you fuckin' with my friend?
