52:44.912 --> 52:45.788
There he is.

52:45.871 --> 52:49.208
You guys got one hell
of a police department around here.

52:49.291 --> 52:51.752
I got a cousin in the department
in New Orleans.

52:51.836 --> 52:54.088
You ever heard of Bob Bouquet?

53:02.429 --> 53:04.598
Put your ass in that chair.

53:08.102 --> 53:11.105
Illegal wiretaps, unauthorized surveillance.

53:12.773 --> 53:13.774
