54:49.245 --> 54:53.666
Down at the morgue, they got a guy
who was not a congregation member.

54:54.917 --> 54:56.418
Alan Singletary.

54:57.378 --> 55:00.840
He's an aide to Senator Harrison.
The Foreign Relations Committee Harrison.

55:00.923 --> 55:05.135
