01:06:39.788 --> 01:06:42.040
We'll wriggle up these two...

01:06:42.583 --> 01:06:44.501
...operative dossiers.

01:06:46.420 --> 01:06:48.714
Start with my friend, Nelson.

01:07:02.394 --> 01:07:04.730
Your friend has had a hell of a career.

01:07:04.813 --> 01:07:08.442
