01:07:40.057 --> 01:07:41.308
Thanks.

01:07:43.852 --> 01:07:45.187
I owe you one.

01:07:45.270 --> 01:07:48.357
- Where are you going?
- I gotta find that priest.

01:07:48.440 --> 01:07:49.858
Be careful.

01:07:53.946 --> 01:07:55.948
{y:i}I find this totally incredulous.

01:07:56.031 --> 01:08:00.452
{y:i}You, being a station chief at the CIA,
{y:i}didn't know what was going on?

01:08:00.536 --> 01:08:02.788
{y:i}Mr. Senator,
{y:i}I'd like to explain a few things.

01:08:02.871 --> 01:08:07.000
