01:13:01.253 --> 01:13:03.172
Do you feel that? Nice?

01:13:04.339 --> 01:13:05.883
You like that?

01:13:09.511 --> 01:13:12.639
Now you're gonna start feeling
something warm.

01:13:12.931 --> 01:13:14.975
Very warm and wonderful.

01:13:15.517 --> 01:13:16.935
